    <text>
        <body xml:lang="fr">
            <!-- PAGINA 16 -->
            <div type="page" n="p016" facs="ms_fr_03951_07_p016">
                
                <!-- TITOLO CAPITOLO 5 -->                
                <p facs="#lb_p016_01">
                    <s type="transcription">
                        <num value="3">3</num> conférence <num value="1">1</num>.
                    </s>

                    <s type="translation">Terza conferenza</s>
                </p>

                <p facs="#lb_p016_03">
                    <s type="transcription" >
                        <emph rend="red"><num value="16">16</num></emph>
                    </s>
                </p>

                <p facs="#lb_p016_02">
                    <s xml:id="TitleCap" type="transcription">§5. La morphologie historique. Le changement morphologique.</s>
                    <s type="translation" xml:id="tradTitleCap">§5. La morfologia storica. Il cambiamento morfologico.</s>
                </p>
                
                <gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="lines" facs="#lb_p016_04"/>                
                
                <!-- PARAGRAFO 1 -->
                <p xml:id="Para1">
                    <s n="linea1" type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_05">
                        Il ressort <emph rend="underlined">indirectement</emph> du §4 qu'il y a dans
                    </s>
                
                    <s n="linea2" type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_06">                        
                        la vie du langage un fait considérable,
                    </s>
                
                    <s n="linea3" type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_07">
                        <add place="margin">
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>d</abbr>
                                <expan>d'une</expan>
                            </choice>
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>import</abbr>
                                <expan>importance</expan>
                            </choice>
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>capit.,</abbr>
                                <expan>capitale,</expan>
                            </choice>
                        </add>
                        qui est le <emph rend="underlined">changement morphologique</emph>.
                    </s>

                    <s type="translation" xml:id="tradPara1">
                        Deriva indirettamente dal § 4 che vi è nella vita del linguaggio un fatto considerevole, d’un’importanza capitale, che è il cambiamento morfologico.
                    </s>
                </p>

                <!-- PARAGRAFO 2-->
                <p xml:id="Para2">
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_08">
                        Et que le procédé que nous avons appelé <emph rend="underlined">morphologie</emph>
                    </s>
                
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_09">
                        <choice>
                            <abbr><emph rend="underlined">rétrosp.</emph></abbr>
                            <expan><emph rend="underlined">rétrospective</emph></expan>
                        </choice>
                        ou
                        <choice>
                            <abbr><emph rend="underlined">anachroniq.</emph></abbr>
                            <expan><emph rend="underlined">anachronique</emph></expan>
                        </choice>
                        ou
                        <choice>
                            <abbr><emph rend="underlined">étymologiq.</emph></abbr>
                            <expan><emph rend="underlined">étymologique</emph></expan>
                        </choice>
                    </s>
                
                    <gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="lines" facs="#lb_p016_10"/>
                
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_11">
                        <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="word" />
                        consiste 
                        <add place="above">
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>tt simpl</abbr>
                                <expan>tout simplement</expan>
                            </choice>
                        </add>
                        à ériger en système
                    </s>
                
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_12">
                        l'oubli
                        <add place="bottom">
                            de ce
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>phén.</abbr>
                                <expan>phénomène</expan>
                            </choice>
                        </add>
                        du changement
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>morphol.</abbr>
                            <expan>morphologique</expan>
                        </choice>
                        .
                    </s>

                    <s type="translation" xml:id="tradPara2">
                        E che il procedimento che noi abbiamo chiamato morfologia retrospettiva o anacronica o etimologica consiste molto semplicemente a erigere a sistema la dimenticanza di tale fenomeno del cambiamento morfologico. 
                    </s>
                </p>

                <!-- PARAGRAFO 3 -->
                <p xml:id="Para3">
                    
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_13">
                        <gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="word" />
                        <del rend="overtyped">Le</del>
                        changement
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>morphologiq</abbr>
                            <expan>morphologique</expan>
                        </choice>
                    </s>
                                        
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_14">
                        <add place="margin">nécessite une étude spéciale qui</add>
                        prend le nom de
                        <emph rend="underlined">
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>Morphol</abbr>
                                <expan>Morphologie</expan>
                            </choice>
                            historique
                        </emph>
                        .
                    </s>
                    
                    <s type="translation" xml:id="tradPara3">
                        Il cambiamento morfologico necessita uno studio speciale, che prende il nome di morfologia storica.
                    </s>
                </p>

                <!-- PARAGRAFO 4 -->
                <p xml:id="Para4">
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_15">
                        Elle sépare les époques et les compare, tandis
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_16">
                        que la 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>morp.</abbr>
                            <expan>morphologie</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        rétrospective les confond.
                    </s>

                    <s type="translation" xml:id="tradPara4">
                        Essa separa le epoche e le mette a confronto, laddove la morfologia retrospettiva le confonde.
                    </s>
                </p>

                <!-- PARAGRAFO 5 -->
                <p xml:id="Para5">
                    
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_17">
                        <num value="2">2</num>
                        Elle 
                        <add>
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>n</abbr>
                                <expan>nous</expan>
                            </choice>
                            présente
                        </add>
                        la véritable perspective entre
                    </s>
                
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_18">
                        les
                        <add place="margin">classifications <num value="1">1</num></add>
                        et les interprétations successives
                        <add place="above">auxquelles</add>
                        <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="word" />
                        la
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_19">
                        langue a pu
                        <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="word" />
                        <gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="word" />
                        <add place="above">
                            se li<del rend="overtyped">vrer</del> sur les
                        </add>
                        mêmes formes,
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_20">
                        tandis que la 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>morp</abbr>
                            <expan>morphologie</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>rétrosp</abbr>
                            <expan>rétrospective</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        cherche,
                        <add place="margin">
                            si
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>vs</abbr>
                                <expan>vous</expan>
                            </choice> 
                            me 
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>permet</abbr>
                                <expan>permettez</expan>
                            </choice>
                            cette
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>img</abbr>
                                <expan>image</expan>
                            </choice>
                            , 
                        </add>
                        à
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_21">
                        obtenir la projection sur un même
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_22">
                        plan 
                        <gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="word" />
                        <add place="bottom">
                            de classifications 
                        </add>
                        très 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>différ.</abbr>
                            <expan>différentes</expan>
                        </choice>
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_23">
                        par leur date.
                    </s>

                    <s type="translation" xml:id="tradPara5">
                        Essa rappresenta la vera prospettiva tra le classificazioni e le interpretazioni successive delle stesse forme alle quali la lingua ha potuto addivenire, mentre la morfologia retrospettiva cerca, se mi permettete quest’immagine, d’ottenere la proiezione su uno stesso piano di classificazioni molto diverse per quanto riguarda la loro data.
                    </s>
                </p>

                <!-- PARAGRAFO 6 -->
                <p xml:id="Para6">

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_24">
                        Elle dira que 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>ds</abbr>
                            <expan>dans</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        <emph rend="underlined">kalb, kalbir,</emph> 
                        par suite
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_25">
                        de la 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>modif.</abbr>
                            <expan>modification</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        du son, le rapport entre l'idée et le
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_26">
                        son est devenu autre que dans leurs 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>protot.</abbr>
                            <expan>prototypes</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        <emph rend="underlined">kalbiz</emph>
                        - 
                        <emph rend="underlined">kalbizō.</emph>
                    </s>

                    <s type="translation" xml:id="tradPara6">
                        Essa dirà che in kalb, kalbir, in seguito alla modificazione del suono, il rapporto tra l’idea e il suono è divenuto altro rispetto ai loro prototipi kalbiz, kalbizo.
                    </s>
                </p>

                <!-- PARAGRAFO 7 -->
                <p xml:id="Para7">
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p016_27">
                        La 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>morp.</abbr>
                            <expan>morphologie</expan>
                        </choice>
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>étym.</abbr>
                            <expan>étymologique</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        ne voit que l'état le 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>+</abbr>
                            <expan>plus</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        primitif et
                    </s>

                    <s type="translation" xml:id="tradPara7">
                        La morfologia etimologica non vede se non lo stato più primitivo e
                    </s>
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- PAGINA 17 -->
            <div type="page" n="p017" facs="ms_fr_03951_07_p017">
                <p xml:id="numpag17">
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p017_01">
                        <num value="17">17</num>
                    </s>
                </p>

                <!-- PARAGRAFO 8 -->
                <p xml:id="Para8">
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p017_02">
                        applique 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>imperturbabl</abbr>
                            <expan>imperturbablement</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        l'analyse
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p017_03">
                        du 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>pre</abbr>
                            <expan>premier</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        jour aux périodes subséquentes.
                    </s>

                    <s type="translation" xml:id="tradPara8">
                        applica imperturbabilmente l’analisi del primo giorno ai periodi susseguenti.
                    </s>
                </p>

                <!-- PARAGRAFO 9 -->
                <p>
                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p017_04">
                        Pas de fusion possible puisque la 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>morp.</abbr>
                            <expan>morphologie</expan>
                        </choice> 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>étymol.</abbr>
                            <expan>étymologique</expan>
                        </choice>
                    </s>

                    <s type="transcription" facs="#lb_p017_05">
                        <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="word" />
                        la négation même du principe 
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>historiq</abbr>
